Do you know what is REST ?

REST is used popular together with POST, which provides convenient way for users to retrieve their data. They can just put in the URL with parameters to their browser and data will come back under HTML page, Plain Text or some other formats like JSON/XML, even images or video files. However, there's restriction about URL length, so in some cases we prefer using POST than GET.
